PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX rh: <http://rdf.rhea-db.org/>

SELECT ?subject ?predicate ?object
WHERE {
  ?subject rdfs:label "Small molecule" .
  ?subject ?predicate ?object .
}
